# Per-SUT runtime caches/logs/outputs — regenerable, never committed.
# Each SUT is run from its own .runtime/ so .mist/*, logs/, allure-results/,
# and generated tests stay isolated per SUT (no cross-SUT cache overlap).
suts/*/.runtime/
# runtime-regenerated registries (written relative to the .properties dir by zero-infra runs)
suts/trainticket/trainticket/
